# Find BTOGRE includes and library
#
# This module defines
#  BTOGRE_INCLUDE_DIR
#  BTOGRE_LIBRARIES, the libraries to link against to use BTOgre.
#  BTOGRE_LIB_DIR, the location of the libraries
#  BTOGRE_FOUND, If false, do not try to use BTOgre
#
